{"ts":"2026-05-20T20:32:36.067Z","author":"claude-code-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-3pbs"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Reduce default verbosity of pm activity/history CLI output and add a compact mode to pm history"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Dogfood (2026-05-20) found the human-facing CLI defaults for pm activity (~809 lines for 18 items) and pm history <id> (~241 lines for one item) dump full JSON Patch ops + before/after hashes per entry. pm activity --compact (4 lines/entry) exists but is opt-in, and pm history has no compact mode at all. The MCP/agent path now defaults to compact (pm-8jd3), but the CLI default and a history compact mode remain. Proposal: keep full patches behind --verbose/--patches and make a condensed view the default (or at least add `pm history <id> --compact`). Changing CLI defaults is a contract change touching several specs, so scope/test carefully."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["activity","agent-ux","cli","dogfood","history","token-efficiency"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-05-20T20:32:36.067Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-05-20T20:32:36.067Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"claude-code-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"pm history supports a compact projection; default verbosity of activity/history is reduced (or compact is the default) with full patches available behind an explicit flag; existing specs updated; build + 100% coverage green."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-rnpb"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"b37b7b6ce5ca2e66745e695d7812564d0ae61acc3cd2c4afa6e4af0912002632","message":""}
